== Edouard Osoque Mendy ==
ni umukinyi ukomeye uzwi cyane muri championa nyinshi zitandukanye yamamaye cyane nka nyezamu

w'ikipe ikomeye muri premier League ariyo [[Ubwongereza|Chelsea]] ndetse n ikipe y'igihugu ya [[Senegali|Senegal]]

Edouard yavutse kuya 1 Werurwe 1992.

== Amateka ==
Edourad yatangiye umwuga we wo gukina mugihugu cy'[[ubufaransa]] aho yakinaga mwishuri rya [[Ubufaransa|Le Havre]]

nyuma yaho gato aza gusinya amasezerao nk'umukinnyi wabigize umwuga mukiciro cya gatatu muri cherbourg

mu mwaka wa 2011. nyuma yaho gato Mendy yaje kwerekeza muri [[Ubufaransa|Marsceille]] muri 2014 ubwo yakomeje kwerekana ubuhangabwe

nku munyezamu ukomeye mu mwaka wa 2020 nibwo yaje gusinya amasezerano mu ikpe ikomeye muri [[Ubwongereza|premier league Chelsea]]

ubwo bamuhayae angana na millioni 22 z'amapawundi muri Championa ye yambere yahise aba umunyezamu wambere

wumuri [[African Jim|Africa]] ukuniye ikipe ikomeye nka [[Ubwongereza|Chelsea]].<ref>https://www.transfermarkt.com/edouard-mendy/profil/spieler/442531</ref>

== Ibihembo ==
Mendy kandi nyuma yo kwigaragaza muri Chelsea yaje kwegukana izina ry'umunyezamu mwiza wa UEFA<ref>https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-10411761/Premier-League-stars-Mohamed-Salah-Edouard-Mendy-miss-FIFAs-Best-XI.html</ref>

ndetse aba umunyezamu Mwiza wa FIFA mumwaka wa 2021 aribwo yabaga umenyezamu wambere

wo muri [[afurika]] wegukanye ibihembo.nyuma yo kwiyegurira Senegal kandi avuye muri Guinea Bisau <ref>https://footballghana.com/ghana-legend-asamoah-gyan-disagrees-with-eduard-mendys-afcon-best-goalkeeper-award</ref>

yabaye umunyezamu mwiza muri championa ya Afurika muri 2019. yafashije kandi igihugu cye gutwara

igkombe muri 2021 arinabwo yabaga umunyezamu mwiza mwirushanwa.

